	<LINE>John Lindsay, Coatbridge ; directors, G. Dalrymple,</LINE>
	<LINE>Duncan Walker, W. Ferguson, W. Gillies, J. Dunlop,</LINE>
	<LINE>R. Ellison, H. Ferry, J. Watson, W. R. Hunter, W.</LINE>
