	<LINE>The objects for which this institution is estabhshed</LINE>
	<LINE>are for the purpose of assisting the members and their</LINE>
	<LINE>widows and families, by settling pensions or granting</LINE>
	<LINE>annuities when so required. Life membership is only</LINE>
	<LINE>five guineas, no further payment. Funds at present</LINE>
	<LINE>amount to £5300, invested in heritable property.</LINE>
